d and revamped.</span><hr size=1> Well, I've been editing what I wrote so far of my novel Datenshi. I've also written a few more parts to it since the last time I posted this story. I've changed a few parts around and tried to correct every possible error. I'd like someone to crit my narrative and to correct me on any errors, both major and minor.<br>
<br>
Oh yeah; contains graphic language (especially in the last part of chapter 2. It'll be censored, though) and violence (though I don't get very descriptive).<br>
